{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","content":"Exit code 1\n\n--- ECE: Perfectly Calibrated Scores ---\n  PASS: Perfect calibration → ECE ≈ 0 (got 0.000000, expected ~0.0)\n  PASS: All bin gaps ≈ 0 for perfect calibration (got 0.000000, expected ~0.0)\n\n--- ECE: Systematically Overconfident ---\n  PASS: Overconfident → ECE > 0.1 (got 0.4)\n  PASS: Overconfident ECE ≈ 0.4 (got 0.400000, expected ~0.4)\n\n--- ECE: Systematically Underconfident ---\n  PASS: Underconfident → ECE > 0.1 (got 0.5)\n\n--- ECE: Edge Cases ---\n  PASS: Empty input → None ECE\n  PASS: Single perfect sample → ECE ≈ 0 (got 0.000000, expected ~0.0)\n  PASS: Mismatched lengths → None ECE\n\n--- ECE: Bin Structure ---\n  PASS: 10 bins generated\n  PASS: All bins have range\n  PASS: All bins have count\n\n--- Dimension ECE ---\n  PASS: Validity ECE computed\n  PASS: Specificity ECE computed\n  PASS: Correctness ECE computed\n  PASS: Overall ECE computed\n  PASS: Validity ECE = 0.06\n  PASS: Specificity ECE = 0.403\n  PASS: validity sample count = 60\n  PASS: validity has sufficient samples\n  PASS: specificity sample count = 60\n  PASS: specificity has sufficient samples\n  PASS: correctness sample count = 60\n  PASS: correctness has sufficient samples\n\n--- Dimension ECE: Insufficient Data ---\n  PASS: validity insufficient with 10 samples\n  PASS: validity count = 10\n  PASS: specificity insufficient with 10 samples\n  PASS: specificity count = 10\n  PASS: correctness insufficient with 10 samples\n  PASS: correctness count = 10\n\n--- Weight Adjustment Bounds ---\n  PASS: validity weight >= 0.1 (got 0.3927)\n  PASS: validity weight <= 0.6 (got 0.3927)\n  PASS: specificity weight >= 0.1 (got 0.2724)\n  PASS: specificity weight <= 0.6 (got 0.2724)\n  PASS: correctness weight >= 0.1 (got 0.3349)\n  PASS: correctness weight <= 0.6 (got 0.3349)\n  PASS: Recommended weights sum to 1.0 (got 1.000000, expected ~1.0)\n  PASS: Deltas present\n  PASS: Auto-apply flag pr